Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Achille Lauro hijack
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xnc5
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 13 Oct 1985
Americans seen to condone Israel attack on PLO following hijacking of Achille Lauro cruise ship. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less